      </a></span><script>(function(d,s,id){var js,stags=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(d.getElementById(id)){return;}js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="http://g-ec2.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/imdb/plugins/rating/js/rating.min.js";stags.parentNode.insertBefore(js,stags);})(document,'script','imdb-rating-api');</script>
      </div>
      <div>
       <p>
         <strong>Nick's Consensus: </strong><i>About Time</i> surprises everyone, including itself, by transcending typical coming-of-age, romance, or familial movies. This spectacularly geniune and touching
          movie mixes humor, fantasy, and grief to communicate an old theme in a completely new light.
       </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div>
  <% if logged_in? %>
    <%= link_to 'New Post', new_post_path %>
  <% end %>
</div>



